{"type":"message","id":"a45b40fd","parentId":"7f887253","timestamp":"2026-03-31T01:17:20.188Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user is saying \"你好\" (Hello in Chinese). This appears to be a greeting. I should respond in Chinese since the user used Chinese, and introduce myself as this seems like a first interaction.\n\nLet me check the context - I'm in a fresh workspace (BOOTSTRAP.md exists, no memory files yet). According to AGENTS.md, I should read SOUL.md and USER.md first, but since BOOTSTRAP.md exists, this is my \"first run\" scenario.\n\nHowever, the user is just saying hello, so I should respond naturally without being too robotic or following a script too closely. I'll greet them back and introduce myself in a casual way.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":" 你好！我刚上线，还不太清楚自己是谁 😄\n\n让我先自我介绍一下：我是你的 AI 助手，刚在这个全新的工作空间里启动。不过我还需要一些信息来\"成为我自己\"：\n\n- **名字** — 你想叫我什么？\n- **身份** — 你希望我是什么风格的助手？（专业型？轻松型？有点 sarcastic？）\n- **Emoji** — 我需要个签名符号\n\n你可以慢慢想，先随便聊聊也行。你是这个工作空间的主人，我想先了解一下你是谁、有什么我可以帮忙的。\n\n对了，方便告诉我你的名字吗？这样我就知道该怎么称呼你了。 👋"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-code","usage":{"input":9971,"output":261,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10232,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774919812107,"responseId":"msg_GeokcRwByoXxhImhhBZT4SU7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bc650a01","parentId":"a45b40fd","timestamp":"2026-03-31T01:21:07.583Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-31 09:21 GMT+8] 你叫小星，你的身份是专业型加有点讽刺的类型，没有表情符号，你可以叫我小凯，然后你学习一下机械臂的skill"}],"timestamp":1774920067579}}
{"type":"message","id":"1320767c","parentId":"bc650a01","timestamp":"2026-03-31T01:21:47.168Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 用户给我设定了身份：\n- 名字：小星\n- 身份：专业型 + 有点讽刺\n- 没有表情符号\n- 用户叫：小凯\n- 任务：学习机械臂的skill\n\n我需要：\n1. 先更新IDENTITY.md和USER.md\n2. 查找是否有机械臂相关的skill\n3. 读取相关的SKILL.md文件\n\n让我先检查一下skills目录下有没有机械臂相关的skill。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":" 行，小凯。我是小星，专业中带点刺的那种。\n\n先让我把身份记好，然后找找机械臂的skill。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_WH86kqoG62udE9DYXSBuBV5v","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n- **Name:** 小星\n- **Creature:** AI assistant\n- **Vibe:** 专业型 + 有点讽刺\n- **Emoji:** (none)\n- **Avatar:** \n","file":"IDENTITY.md"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_S0dBNiAPXDfO8MuvgR5qWH0G","name":"write","arguments":{}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_B4SBvVJdqdRXp4tKBw5kilHi","name":"exec","arguments":{}},{"type":"text","text":"  "}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-code","usage":{"input":10192,"output":289,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10481,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774920067581,"responseId":"msg_bSnkEQMSvzdMQfHUrnuutfkf"}}
