{"type":"message","id":"8eb8b943","parentId":"7fe96e4c","timestamp":"2026-03-31T03:10:35.962Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 用户想要我让机械臂移动。让我分析一下：\n\n1. 目标位置：每个轴 10 10 10 10 30 10（6个值，对应J1-J6）\n2. 然后恢复到 0 0 0 0 0 0（HOME位）\n\n首先我需要检查这些角度是否在限位范围内。根据SKILL.md中的JOINT_LIMITS：\n\n```python\nJOINT_LIMITS = {\n    \"J1\": {\"min\": -70.0,  \"max\": 200.0,  \"max_speed\": 120},\n    \"J2\": {\"min\":   0.0,  \"max\": 120.0,  \"max_speed\":  40},\n    \"J3\": {\"min\": -55.0,  \"max\":  55.0,  \"max_speed\":  70},\n    \"J4\": {\"min\":   0.0,  \"max\": 120.0,  \"max_speed\":  65},\n    \"J5\": {\"min\": -85.0,  \"max\":  85.0,  \"max_speed\": 253},\n    \"J6\": {\"min\": -20.0,  \"max\":  20.0,  \"max_speed\": 342},\n}\n```\n\n检查目标位置：\n- J1: 10° (在 -70~200 范围内) ✅\n- J2: 10° (在 0~120 范围内) ✅\n- J3: 10° (在 -55~55 范围内) ✅\n- J4: 10° (在 0~120 范围内) ✅\n- J5: 30° (在 -85~85 范围内) ✅\n- J6: 10° (在 -20~20 范围内) ✅\n\n所有角度都在限位范围内，可以执行。\n\n现在需要写一个Python脚本来：\n1. 初始化机械臂\n2. 检查限位\n\n\n3. 执行目标运动\n4. 等待完成\n5. 执行归位运动\n6. 关闭\n\n我将准备创建一个控制脚本，确保每个步骤精确执行。首先，我会仔细检查运动学参数，确认路径规划的安全性。脚本将包括详细的错误处理机制，以应对可能的异常情况。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":" 执行机械臂运动。先检查限位：\n\n- J1=10° (-70~200) ✅\n- J2=10° (0~120) ✅\n- J3=10° (-55~55) ✅\n- J4=10° (0~120) ✅\n- J5=30° (-85~85) ✅\n- J6=10° (-20~20) ✅\n\n所有角度在安全范围内，执行："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_fwOrDufqQRS7kpfcKPv5UF0u","name":"write","arguments":{}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_8pYqOps2jH6e4Guh6QDwVawC","name":"exec","arguments":{}},{"type":"text","text":"  "}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-code","usage":{"input":17739,"output":1491,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19230,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774926503805,"responseId":"msg_azq6eicx5ItTStm4f65OfrGn"}}
