{"type":"message","id":"a1a89a7c","parentId":"13d355f8","timestamp":"2026-03-31T03:21:00.392Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"                   机器人IP可以ping通，说明网络连接正常。问题可能在于SDK初始化或连接过程。\n\n让我查看工作空间中是否有示例代码可以参考。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"  网络连接正常（192.168.3.100可ping通）。让我查看现有的测试代码："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_BID8SuOT9jNpfAFdK6CC78AI","name":"read","arguments":{}},{"type":"text","text":"  "}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-code","usage":{"input":34,"output":75,"cacheRead":26688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26797,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774927248940,"responseId":"msg_SvWwn8WYKjUJsbnmeT0rZmct"}}
