{"type":"message","id":"8f0ebb91","parentId":"e56d55d4","timestamp":"2026-03-31T03:42:51.349Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 用户发送了\"new\"，可能是在测试或重新开始。让我看看当前状态。\n\n之前我尝试控制机械臂，但遇到了一些问题：\n1. 直接使用PallasSDK时出现段错误\n2. 使用ROS2接口时缺少arm_control_interface模块\n\n让我总结一下当前情况并询问用户。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"   收到。让我总结一下当前情况：\n\n---\n\n**执行状态：**\n\n我之前尝试让机械臂运动（目标位置 [10,10,10,10,30,10] → 归位 [0,0,0,0,0,0]），但遇到了一些问题：\n\n| 尝试方式 | 结果 | 问题 |\n|---------|------|------|\n| PallasSDK直连 | ❌ 段错误 | SDK连接时崩溃 |\n| ROS2接口 | ❌ 模块缺失 | 找不到 `arm_control_interface` |\n\n**可能原因：**\n1. 机器人底层未启动 (`ros2 launch robot_bringup robot.launch.py`)\n2. CAN总线未配置\n3. 需要先启动机械臂驱动节点\n\n---\n\n**你需要确认：**\n\n1. **机器人底层已启动？** 需要运行：\n   ```bash\n   source ~/Haier_robot_ws/install/setup.bash\n   ros2 launch robot_bringup robot.launch.py\n   ```\n\n2. **CAN总线已配置？** 需要执行：\n   ```bash\n   sudo ip link set can0 down\n   sudo ip link set can0 type can bitrate 1000000\n   sudo ip link set can0 up\n   ```\n\n3. **机械臂驱动节点在运行？** 检查：\n   ```bash\n   ros2 node list | grep arm\n   ```\n\n请确认以上步骤已完成，我再执行运动指令。或者你可以直接运行工作空间里现有的测试脚本：\n```bash\ncd ~/Haier_robot_ws\npython3 build/hair_arm_control/build/lib.linux-aarch64-cpython-310/hair_arm_control/opt/opt_api_test.py\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-code","usage":{"input":48396,"output":407,"cacheRead":9152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57955,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774928543518,"responseId":"msg_7OiPTnja5C86vTluCociGMqC"}}
